<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>LaptopShop- VH </title>
    <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport">
    <meta content="" name="keywords">
    <meta content="" name="description">

    <!-- Favicon: Turtle -->
    <link rel="icon" href="/client/favicon.svg?v=1" type="image/svg+xml">
    <link rel="alternate icon" href="/client/favicon.ico">
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/client/apple-touch-icon.png">
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#2e7d32">
    <!-- Favicon: Turtle (bự & rõ) -->
    <link rel="icon" href="/client/favicon.svg?v=3" sizes="any" type="image/svg+xml">
    <link rel="icon" href="/client/favicon-32.png" sizes="120x120"> <!-- (tuỳ chọn) -->

    <!-- Google Web Fonts -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:wght@400;600&family=Raleway:wght@600;800&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- Icon Font Stylesheet -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.15.4/css/all.css" />
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.4.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- Libraries Stylesheet -->
    <link href="/client/lib/lightbox/css/lightbox.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/client/lib/owlcarousel/assets/owl.carousel.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- Customized Bootstrap Stylesheet -->
    <link href="/client/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- Template Stylesheet -->
    <link href="/client/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery-toast-plugin/1.3.2/jquery.toast.min.css"
        integrity="sha512-wJgJNTBBkLit7ymC6vvzM1EcSWeM9mmOu+1USHaRBbHkm6W9EgM0HY27+UtUaprntaYQJF75rc8gjxllKs5OIQ=="
        crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
    <!-- Swiper CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/swiper@11/swiper-bundle.min.css" />

    <!-- Swiper JS -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/swiper@11/swiper-bundle.min.js"></script>
    <link href="/client/css/home/show.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>

    </style>

</head>


<body>

    <!-- Spinner Start -->
    <div id="spinner"
        class="show w-100 vh-100 bg-white position-fixed translate-middle top-50 start-50  d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
        <div class="spinner-grow text-primary" role="status"></div>
    </div>
    <!-- Spinner End -->

    <!-- Navbar start -->
    <%- include('../layout/header'); -%>
        <!-- Navbar End -->

        <!-- Hero Start -->
        <%- include('../layout/banner'); -%>
            <!-- Hero End -->


            <!-- Sản phẩm khuyến mãi -->


            <div class="container-fluid">
                <div class="container ">
                    <div class="tab-class text-center">
                        <div class="row g-4">
                            <section class="mt-5">
                                <h2 class="fire-title-wrapper ">
                                    <span class="fire-title ">
                                        <img src="https://media2.giphy.com/media/v1.Y2lkPTc5MGI3NjExcmJqeW0xZ2Nsc3o5Z245amhwdXozY3NlbGQyanFycXd3OG1ycG9ybSZlcD12MV9pbnRlcm5hbF9naWZfYnlfaWQmY3Q9Zw/KPVJXH61g2jHkdqZES/giphy.gif"
                                            alt="fire" class="fire-gif"> <span>Sản phẩm khuyến
                                            mãi</span> </span>
                                    <video autoplay loop muted playsinline class="fire-bg">
                                        <source src="https://i.imgur.com/J6J4pP6.mp4" type="video/mp4">
                                    </video>
                                </h2>
                                <!-- Swiper container -->
                                <div class="swiper promo-swiper">
                                    <div class="swiper-wrapper">
                                        <% promoProducts.forEach(p=> { %>
                                            <div class="swiper-slide">
                                                <div
                                                    class="card h-100 shadow-lg border-0 promo-card position-relative overflow-hidden">

                                                    <!-- Hình ảnh -->
                                                    <div class="promo-img-wrapper">
                                                        <img src="/images/product/<%= p.image %>"
                                                            class="card-img-top promo-img" alt="<%= p.name %>">
                                                    </div>

                                                    <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
                                                        <h5 class="card-title text-truncate fw-bold">
                                                            <%= p.name %>
                                                        </h5>
                                                        <p class="mb-1 text-decoration-line-through text-muted small">
                                                            <%= p.price.toLocaleString('vi-VN') %> ₫
                                                                <!-- Badge giảm giá -->
                                                                <span
                                                                    class="badge bg-danger position-absolute promo-badge"
                                                                    style="margin-left: 10px; margin-top: 2px;">
                                                                    -<%= p.discount %>%
                                                                </span>
                                                        </p>
                                                        <p class="fw-bold text-danger fs-5 mb-3">
                                                            <%= (p.price * (100 - p.discount) /
                                                                100).toLocaleString('vi-VN') %> ₫
                                                        </p>

                                                        <div class="mt-auto text-center">
                                                            <a href="/product/<%= p.id %>"
                                                                class="btn btn-success rounded-pill px-4">
                                                                <i class="fa fa-eye me-2"></i> Xem
                                                                chi tiết
                                                            </a>
                                                        </div>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <% }) %>
                                    </div>

                                    <!-- Nút điều hướng -->
                                    <div class="swiper-button-next"></div>
                                    <div class="swiper-button-prev"></div>

                                    <!-- Thanh pagination -->
                                    <div class="swiper-pagination" hidden></div>
                                </div>
                            </section>

                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Sản phẩm khuyến mãi -->


            <!-- Fruits Shop Start-->
            <div class="container-fluid ">
                <div class="container ">
                    <div class="tab-class text-center">
                        <div class="row g-4">
                            <div class="col-lg-4 text-start">
                                <h1>Sản phẩm nổi bật</h1>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-lg-8 text-end">
                                <ul class="nav nav-pills d-inline-flex text-center mb-5">
                                    <li class="nav-item">
                                        <a class="d-flex m-2 py-2 btn btn-success rounded-pill active" href="/products">
                                            <span class="text-light" style="width: 130px;">Tất cả sản
                                                phẩm</span>
                                        </a>
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="tab-content">
                            <div id="tab-1" class="tab-pane fade show p-0 active">
                                <div class="row g-4">
                                    <div class="col-lg-12">
                                        <div class="row g-4">
                                            <% products.forEach( function (product) { %>
                                                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 col-xl-3">
                                                    <div class="rounded position-relative fruite-item">
                                                        <div class="fruite-img">
                                                            <img src="/images/product/<%= product.image %>"
                                                                class="img-fluid w-100 rounded-top" alt="">
                                                        </div>
                                                        <div class="text-white bg-secondary px-3 py-1 rounded position-absolute"
                                                            style="top: 10px; left: 10px;">Laptop</div>
                                                        <div class="p-4 border  border-top-0 rounded-bottom">
                                                            <h4 style="font-size: 18px;">
                                                                <a href="/product/<%= product.id %>">
                                                                    <%= product.name %>
                                                                </a>

                                                            </h4>
                                                            <p style="font-size: 15px;">
                                                                <%= product.shortDesc %>
                                                            </p>
                                                            <% const __avg=Number(product?.ratingAvg ?? 0); const
                                                                __count=Number(product?.ratingCount ?? 0); const
                                                                __rounded=Math.round(__avg * 2) / 2; // làm tròn 0.5
                                                                const __full=Math.floor(__rounded); const
                                                                __half=(__rounded - __full)===0.5 ? 1 : 0; const
                                                                __empty=5 - __full - __half; %>
                                                                <div class="mb-2 text-center">
                                                                    <span class="rating-stars"
                                                                        title="<%= __avg.toFixed(1) %>/5">
                                                                        <% for (let i=0; i < __full; i++) { %><i
                                                                                class="fas fa-star"></i>
                                                                            <% } %>
                                                                                <% if (__half) { %><i
                                                                                        class="fas fa-star-half-alt"></i>
                                                                                    <% } %>
                                                                                        <% for (let i=0; i < __empty;
                                                                                            i++) { %><i
                                                                                                class="far fa-star"></i>
                                                                                            <% } %>
                                                                                                <span class="count">(<%=
                                                                                                        __count %>
                                                                                                        )</span>
                                                                    </span>
                                                                </div>

                                                                <div
                                                                    class="d-flex justify-content-center flex-lg-wrap row">
                                                                    <% if (product.discount> 0) { %>
                                                                        <!-- Giá gốc -->
                                                                        <div
                                                                            class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
                                                                            <p class="mb-1 text-decoration-line-through text-muted small me-2"
                                                                                style="font-size: 12px;">
                                                                                <%= new Intl.NumberFormat('vi-VN', {
                                                                                    style: 'currency' , currency: 'VND'
                                                                                    }).format(product.price) %>
                                                                            </p>

                                                                            <span class="badge bg-danger"
                                                                                style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                                                                                -<%= product.discount %>%
                                                                            </span>
                                                                        </div>



                                                                        <!-- Giá sau giảm + % giảm -->
                                                                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center"
                                                                            style="margin-bottom: 30px;">
                                                                            <p
                                                                                class="fw-bold text-danger fs-5 mb-0 me-2">
                                                                                <%= new Intl.NumberFormat('vi-VN', {
                                                                                    style: 'currency' , currency: 'VND'
                                                                                    }).format(product.price * (100 -
                                                                                    product.discount) / 100) %>
                                                                            </p>

                                                                        </div>

                                                                        <% } else { %>
                                                                            <!-- Giá thường -->
                                                                            <div class="text-dark fs-5 fw-bold mb-3 text-center w-100 "
                                                                                style="padding-bottom: 15px;">
                                                                                <%= new Intl.NumberFormat('vi-VN', {
                                                                                    style: 'currency' , currency: 'VND'
                                                                                    }).format(product.price) %>
                                                                            </div>
                                                                            <% } %>

                                                                                <!-- Nút thêm vào giỏ + tồn kho -->
                                                                                <div
                                                                                    class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mt-1 w-100">
                                                                                    <form onsubmit="return false;">
                                                                                        <button type="button"
                                                                                            data-product-id="<%= product.id %>"
                                                                                            class="btnAddToCartHomePage mx-auto btn border rounded-pill px-3 text-primary">
                                                                                            <i
                                                                                                class="fa fa-shopping-bag me-2 text-primary"></i>
                                                                                            Thêm vào giỏ
                                                                                        </button>
                                                                                    </form>
                                                                                    <span
                                                                                        class="badge bg-primary ms-3">Còn:
                                                                                        <%= product.quantity %>
                                                                                    </span>
                                                                                </div>

                                                                </div>

                                                        </div>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                                <% }) %>
                                                    <div class="pagination d-flex justify-content-center mt-5">
                                                        <!-- Nút Previous -->
                                                        <li
                                                            class="<%= page === 1 ? 'disabled page-item' : 'page-item' %> ">
                                                            <a class="page-link" href="/?page=<%= page - 1 %>"
                                                                aria-label="Previous">
                                                                <span aria-hidden="true">&laquo;</span>
                                                            </a>
                                                        </li>

                                                        <% function getPagination(current, total) { const pages=[];
                                                            const range=(start, end)=> {
                                                            const arr = [];
                                                            for (let i = start; i <= end; i++) arr.push(i); return arr;
                                                                }; if (total <=7) return range(1, total); const left=1;
                                                                const right=1; pages.push(...range(1, left)); if
                                                                (current> left + 2) {
                                                                pages.push("...");
                                                                }

                                                                const start = Math.max(current - 1, left + 1);
                                                                const end = Math.min(current + 1, total - right);
                                                                for (let i = start; i <= end; i++) { pages.push(i); } if
                                                                    (current < total - right - 1) { pages.push("..."); }
                                                                    pages.push(...range(total - right + 1, total));
                                                                    return pages; } const pagination=getPagination(page,
                                                                    totalPages); %>

                                                                    <% pagination.forEach(p=> { %>
                                                                        <% if (p==="..." ) { %>
                                                                            <li class="page-item disabled"><span
                                                                                    class="page-link">...</span></li>
                                                                            <% } else { %>
                                                                                <li class="page-item">
                                                                                    <a class="page-link <%= page === p ? 'active' : '' %>"
                                                                                        href="/?page=<%= p %>">
                                                                                        <%= p %>
                                                                                    </a>
                                                                                </li>
                                                                                <% } %>
                                                                                    <% }) %>

                                                                                        <!-- Nút Next -->
                                                                                        <li
                                                                                            class="<%= page === totalPages ? 'disabled page-item' : 'page-item' %> ">
                                                                                            <a class="page-link"
                                                                                                href="/?page=<%= page + 1 %>"
                                                                                                aria-label="Next">
                                                                                                <span
                                                                                                    aria-hidden="true">&raquo;</span>
                                                                                            </a>
                                                                                        </li>
                                                    </div>

                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Fruits Shop End-->

            <!-- Hướng dẫn mua laptop (pro) -->
            <div class="container-fluid py-5 guide-wrap">
                <div class="container">
                    <section id="buying-guide"
                        class="rounded-4 shadow-lg position-relative overflow-hidden p-4 p-md-5 bg-white">
                        <!-- Header -->
                        <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-md-row align-items-md-center justify-content-between mb-4">
                            <div>
                                <div class="text-uppercase small fw-semibold text-success opacity-75">Buying Guide
                                </div>
                                <h2 class="mb-1">Hướng dẫn mua laptop chuẩn chuyên gia</h2>
                                <div class="text-muted">Chọn theo ngân sách, nhu cầu hoặc cấu hình đề xuất — nhanh,
                                    dễ, chuẩn.</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mt-3 mt-md-0">
                                <a href="/products" class="btn btn-success rounded-pill px-4">
                                    <i class="fa fa-laptop me-2"></i> Xem tất cả laptop
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- 3 khối chính -->
                        <div class="row g-3 g-lg-4">
                            <!-- Theo ngân sách -->
                            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                                <div class="guide-card h-100 p-4 rounded-4 border">
                                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
                                        <span class="icon-pill me-2"><i class="fa fa-wallet"></i></span>
                                        <h5 class="mb-0">Chọn theo ngân sách</h5>
                                    </div>
                                    <p class="text-muted mb-3">Tối ưu chi phí theo mức giá bạn muốn.</p>
                                    <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                                        <!-- dùng chip để đẩy câu hỏi vào chat AI của bạn -->
                                        <button class="chip" type="button"
                                            data-q="Tư vấn laptop dưới 12 triệu, ưu tiên RAM 16GB">≤ 12
                                            triệu</button>
                                        <button class="chip" type="button"
                                            data-q="Tư vấn laptop 12–20 triệu cho văn phòng, nhẹ pin trâu">12–20
                                            triệu</button>
                                        <button class="chip" type="button"
                                            data-q="Tư vấn laptop 20–30 triệu cho đồ họa nhẹ, màn đẹp">20–30
                                            triệu</button>
                                        <button class="chip" type="button"
                                            data-q="Laptop cao cấp trên 30 triệu, build tốt, màn 100% sRGB">≥ 30
                                            triệu</button>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- Theo nhu cầu -->
                            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                                <div class="guide-card h-100 p-4 rounded-4 border">
                                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
                                        <span class="icon-pill me-2"><i class="fa fa-bullseye"></i></span>
                                        <h5 class="mb-0">Chọn theo nhu cầu</h5>
                                    </div>
                                    <p class="text-muted mb-3">Ưu tiên đúng việc để hiệu quả nhất.</p>
                                    <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                                        <button class="chip" type="button"
                                            data-q="Tư vấn laptop văn phòng nhẹ dưới 1.3kg, pin tốt">Văn
                                            phòng</button>
                                        <button class="chip" type="button"
                                            data-q="Tư vấn laptop cho sinh viên IT, ưu tiên RAM 16GB và SSD 512GB">Sinh
                                            viên IT</button>
                                        <button class="chip" type="button"
                                            data-q="Tư vấn laptop gaming 20–30 triệu, RTX 4050 trở lên">Gaming</button>
                                        <button class="chip" type="button"
                                            data-q="Tư vấn laptop đồ họa/creator màn đẹp 100% sRGB">Đồ họa</button>
                                        <button class="chip" type="button"
                                            data-q="Tư vấn ultrabook mỏng nhẹ dưới 1.2kg, sạc Type-C">Mỏng
                                            nhẹ</button>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- Cấu hình đề xuất -->
                            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-4">
                                <div class="guide-card h-100 p-4 rounded-4 border">
                                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
                                        <span class="icon-pill me-2"><i class="fa fa-microchip"></i></span>
                                        <h5 class="mb-0">Cấu hình đề xuất nhanh</h5>
                                    </div>

                                    <ul class="list-unstyled mb-0 small">
                                        <li class="mb-2"><i class="fa fa-check text-success me-2"></i>Văn phòng:
                                            Core i5 / Ryzen 5 • RAM ≥ 16GB • SSD ≥ 512GB</li>
                                        <li class="mb-2"><i class="fa fa-check text-success me-2"></i>Gaming: i5/i7
                                            + RTX 4050↑ • RAM 16–32GB • tản tốt</li>
                                        <li class="mb-2"><i class="fa fa-check text-success me-2"></i>Đồ họa: i7/R7
                                            • RTX 4060↑ • Màn ≥ 100% sRGB/IPS hoặc OLED</li>
                                        <li class="mb-2"><i class="fa fa-check text-success me-2"></i>Di động: ≤
                                            1.3kg • pin ≥ 50Wh • sạc USB-C PD</li>
                                        <li><i class="fa fa-check text-success me-2"></i>Ưu tiên Wi-Fi 6/6E, bàn
                                            phím tốt, bảo hành chính hãng</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Divider -->
                        <hr class="my-4 my-lg-5 divider">

                        <!-- Accordion chi tiết -->
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-lg-8">
                                <div class="accordion guide-accordion" id="guideAccordion">
                                    <div class="accordion-item">
                                        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="cpuHead">
                                            <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                                                data-bs-target="#cpu">
                                                CPU & RAM
                                            </button>
                                        </h2>
                                        <div id="cpu" class="accordion-collapse collapse show"
                                            data-bs-parent="#guideAccordion">
                                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                                <p class="mb-2">CPU quyết định tốc độ xử lý; RAM quyết định độ mượt
                                                    khi đa nhiệm.</p>
                                                <ul class="small mb-0">
                                                    <li>Văn phòng: <strong>Intel Core i5 / Ryzen 5</strong>, RAM
                                                        <strong>16GB</strong>.
                                                    </li>
                                                    <li>Đồ họa/Gaming: <strong>Core i7 / Ryzen 7</strong>, RAM
                                                        <strong>16–32GB</strong>.
                                                    </li>
                                                </ul>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="accordion-item">
                                        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="gpuHead">
                                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
                                                data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#gpu">
                                                GPU & Màn hình
                                            </button>
                                        </h2>
                                        <div id="gpu" class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                                            data-bs-parent="#guideAccordion">
                                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                                <ul class="small mb-0">
                                                    <li>Gaming/3D: <strong>RTX 4050</strong> trở lên.</li>
                                                    <li>Thiết kế: màn <strong>100% sRGB</strong> trở lên, ưu tiên
                                                        <strong>IPS/OLED</strong>, 300 nits+.
                                                    </li>
                                                    <li>Tần số quét 120–165Hz giúp cuộn/điều hướng mượt hơn.</li>
                                                </ul>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="accordion-item">
                                        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="storageHead">
                                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
                                                data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#storage">
                                                Lưu trữ & Pin
                                            </button>
                                        </h2>
                                        <div id="storage" class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                                            data-bs-parent="#guideAccordion">
                                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                                <ul class="small mb-0">
                                                    <li><strong>SSD ≥ 512GB</strong> cho trải nghiệm nhanh; cân nhắc
                                                        khe trống để nâng cấp.</li>
                                                    <li>Pin: 50–70Wh là ngưỡng tốt; sạc <strong>USB-C PD</strong>
                                                        tiện dùng chung.</li>
                                                </ul>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="accordion-item">
                                        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="buildHead">
                                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button"
                                                data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#build">
                                                Trọng lượng & Độ bền
                                            </button>
                                        </h2>
                                        <div id="build" class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                                            data-bs-parent="#guideAccordion">
                                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                                <ul class="small mb-0">
                                                    <li>Di động nhiều: trọng lượng <strong>≤ 1.3kg</strong>.</li>
                                                    <li>Vỏ kim loại, bản lề chắc; bàn phím có đèn nền, hành trình
                                                        ổn.</li>
                                                </ul>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- Checklist nhanh + CTA -->
                            <div class="col-lg-4 mt-4 mt-lg-0">
